  "prompt": "Where is a reliable mobile repair shop to get my phone screen replaced in Kolkata?",
  "response": "Finding a reliable mobile repair shop in Kolkata to replace your phone screen is crucial to ensure quality service and genuine parts. Here are some reputable options you can consider:\n\n### 1. **iCare Service Center**\n- **Specialization:** Primarily Apple products, but also services other major brands.\n- **Reputation:** Known for high-quality repairs and excellent customer service.\n- **Locations:** Multiple outlets across Kolkata, including Salt Lake and Esplanade.\n- **Contact:** [Visit their website](https://icare.com/) for specific addresses and contact details.\n\n### 2. **Kontaktinfosys**\n- **Specialization:** Wide range of smartphone brands including Samsung, Xiaomi, OnePlus, and more.\n- **Reputation:** Trusted for reliable repairs and use of original parts.\n- **Locations:** Available in major areas like Salt Lake, Gariahat, and Park Street.\n- **Contact:** Check their [official website](https://kontaktinfosys.com/) for branch details.\n\n### 3. **The Mobile Centre**\n- **Specialization:** Comprehensive mobile repairs including screen replacements, battery issues, and more.\n- **Reputation:** Offers warranty on parts and labor, ensuring peace of mind.\n- **Locations:** Multiple locations including EM Bypass and Sealdah.\n- **Contact:** Visit [The Mobile Centre](http://themobilecentre.com/) for more information.\n\n### 4. **Gadget Magic**\n- **Specialization:** Specialists in screen replacements, water damage repairs, and software issues.\n- **Reputation:** Positive reviews for quick turnaround times and professional service.\n- **Locations:** Located in areas like New Market and Rajabazar.\n- **Contact:** Look up Gadget Magic on Google Maps for directions and contact info.\n\n### 5. **RepairStore24**\n- **Specialization:** Offers a wide array of services including screen repairs, hardware issues, and software troubleshooting.\n- **Reputation:** Known for friendly staff and reliable service quality.\n- **Locations:** Available in regions like Ballygunge and Howrah.\n- **Contact:** Visit their [website](https://repairstore24.com/) for more details.\n\n### 6. **Authorized Service Centers**\nIf your phone is still under warranty or you prefer official service, consider visiting the brand\u2019s authorized service center:\n- **Samsung Authorized Service Center**\n- **Apple Authorized Service Providers**\n- **OnePlus Authorized Centers**\n- **Xiaomi Mi Service Centers**\n\n**Where to Find These Centers:**\n- **Bhawanipur:** Many authorized centers are located here.\n- **Salt Lake Sector V:** A hub for various brand-specific service centers.\n- **Park Street and Esplanade:** Central locations with multiple service options.\n\n### **Tips for Choosing the Right Repair Shop:**\n\n1. **Check Reviews:** Look up customer reviews on Google, Justdial, or Yelp to gauge the reliability and quality of service.\n2. **Verify Parts Quality:** Ensure that the shop uses genuine or high-quality replacement parts to avoid future issues.\n3. **Warranty on Repairs:** Opt for shops that offer a warranty on both parts and labor.\n4. **Compare Prices:** Get quotes from multiple shops to ensure you\u2019re getting a fair price.\n5. **Ask About Turnaround Time:** If you need your phone urgently, inquire about how long the repair will take.\n\n### **Popular Areas in Kolkata for Mobile Repairs:**\n- **Salt Lake Sector V**\n- **Gariahat**\n- **Park Street**\n- **New Market**\n- **Rajabazar**\n- **Ballygunge**\n\n### **Final Advice:**\nBefore handing over your phone for repair, **back up your data** to prevent any loss. Also, ensure you receive a **receipt or service agreement** outlining the repair details and warranties provided.\n\nBy considering the options and tips above, you should be able to find a reliable mobile repair shop in Kolkata to replace your phone screen efficiently and securely.",
